data.title: Manolo's Mixtape, 20 Years of Chocolate
data.description: The magnificent Manolo with another mixtape masterpiece spanning the first 20 years of Chocolate Skateboards. Featuring the entire Chocolate team and pulling from Goldfish, Paco, Mouse, The Chocolate Tour, Hot Chocolate, Fully Flared, Pretty Sweet as well as other rare and unseen footage.
